    A value of "Off" will cycle the existing colour palette. Other values will mean that a new palette for green will be algorithmically generated.

    The keyboard shortcut is @{b}w@{ub} to go forward through the cycle gadget's choices.
    The keyboard shortcut is @{b}W@{ub} to go backward through the cycle gadget's choices.
@endnode

@node Gad_GreenPhaseString "ColourCycle Gadgets"
@{b}Green Phase Value:@{ub}

    The current value for the green phase offset is shown here.
    This gadget has a range of 0 to 359. It has a default value of 0.

    This gadget has no keyboard shortcut.
@endnode

