@{b}Green Speed Value:@{ub}

    The current value for the green wave speed is shown here.
    This gadget has a range of 0.000 to 359.975 in steps of 0.025. It has a default value of 0.750.

    This gadget has no keyboard shortcut.
@endnode

@node Gad_GreenLenSlider "ColourCycle Gadgets"
@{b}Green Speed Slider:@{ub}

    This slider will allow you to change the green wave speed.
    This gadget has a range of 0.000 to 359.975 in steps of 0.025. It has a default value of 0.750.

    The keyboard shortcut is @{b}s@{ub} to increase the value.
    The keyboard shortcut is @{b}S@{ub} to decrease the value.
@endnode

@node Gad_GreenMeanString "ColourCycle Gadgets"
@{b}Green Mean Value:@{ub}

    The current value for the green mean is shown here.
    This gadget has a range of 0 to 255. It has a default value of 127.

    This gadget has no keyboard shortcut.
@endnode

