@{b}Blue Speed Value:@{ub}

    The current value for the blue wave speed is shown here.
    This gadget has a range of 0.000 to 359.975 in steps of 0.025. It has a default value of 0.625.

    This gadget has no keyboard shortcut.
@endnode

@node Gad_BlueLenSlider "ColourCycle Gadgets"
@{b}Blue Speed Slider:@{ub}

    This slider will allow you to change the blue wave speed.
    This gadget has a range of 0.000 to 359.975 in steps of 0.025. It has a default value of 0.625.

